    "story_name": "暗影下的少女第2话 黄衣之村",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人目睹了大量哈斯塔聚集的景象。\\n那便是渴求不老不死的村民们的末路。\\n他们因诡异的景象而决定离开村子，\\n然而为时已晚，\\n无数哈斯塔包围了他们。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈斯塔",
            "context": "啊噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "哈斯塔？他在做什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "喂，库格尔，你看那个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那个？喂喂！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "怎么有这么多哈斯塔……\\n这到底是怎么回事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈斯塔？",
            "context": "咕呜呜呜……咕呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那家伙……很痛苦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈斯塔？",
            "context": "噢噢噢！啊噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈斯塔？",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "这边都开始自相残杀了。\\n这到底是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "嗯！？那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那不是白天得到什么\\n哈斯塔祝福的老爷子嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "啊……身体……呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "喂、喂，老爷子。\\n怎么了，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "为什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "哈？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "为什么……老夫……明明得到了\\n哈斯塔大人的……祝福……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "呜呜呜呜呜啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "老、老爷子！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120021_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民",
            "context": "啊啦哇啊呀吧啦啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01",
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "老爷子……变成哈斯塔了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这就是哈斯塔祝福的真相吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民？",
            "context": "咕嘎啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "唔噢！？竟然攻击我们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "与其说是攻击……\\n似乎只是在发狂……怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "麻烦不请自来也不能不管……\\n啧，真难应付……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊\\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊\\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "呃！？这是什么声音！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "吼声……不，嚎叫？\\n从哪里传来的……是谁……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210105_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村民？",
            "context": "啊、啊啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事？这群家伙怎么突然\\n开始一起朝某个方向移动了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "是在……被谁呼唤吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "他们是哈斯塔的仆从……\\n已经是背负了无法逃脱的\\n宿命的祭品了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "阿加莎！？\\n这出闹剧到底是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "二位真是不应该……\\n我还特意忠告过二位\\n不要在夜晚出门的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "忠告啊……我听着倒像是煽动，\\n是我多想了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "谁知道呢……\\n不过，我可是衷心地\\n不想让二位受伤哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那真是感激不尽，\\n但我们可不是会害怕得\\n在妈妈怀里颤抖的小孩子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "先不说这个，\\n那些家伙到底是怎么回事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "我可是看见那个得到\\n什么哈斯塔祝福的老爷子\\n变得跟哈斯塔一模一样了啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "那是渴求永恒之人的\\n可悲末路……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "果然……那就是不老不死\\n传闻的真相吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "不老不死……是不惜变成那样\\n也想得到的东西吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "这村子其实是被哈斯塔\\n囚禁的村子……追求永恒的人\\n都只有沦为黄衣奴仆这一条路。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那个哈斯塔……\\n为什么要做这种事？\\n别告诉我是出于慈悲之心啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "有一扇门，那是用来\\n迎接心爱之人的巨大门扉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "哈？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "但是，如果那扇门被上了锁，\\n二位会怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "你是说……\\n哈斯塔在寻找开锁的钥匙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "而且还大肆聚集了\\n这么多无辜之人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "这个村子里只有囚徒，\\n这是我唯一能告诉你们的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "永恒、崇拜、思慕、执念。\\n任何人都会被某些事物所囚禁。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "至少我会为你们祈祷，\\n愿你们不会被囚禁……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "还是说……其实你们\\n已经被囚禁了呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "怎么了，海因瓦尔德？\\n脸色这么难看。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我总有种不祥的预感，\\n看来还是尽早离开这村子为妙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "我虽然也有同感……不过真难得啊，\\n我还以为你反而想留下呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "倒不是提不起兴趣，\\n但麻烦事似乎会更多。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "也是……\\n天一亮我们就离开村子吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "拉托妮？怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "来、来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "来了？你是指什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我不知道……但是，好可怕……\\n有什么……要来了！不、不要……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110281_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "嗯！？怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110280_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "糟了……库格尔。\\n你看外面……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_21303_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
